    <h1>Global Warming</h1>
    <p>
        Global warming refers to the long-term rise in Earth's average surface temperature due to human activities, primarily the release of greenhouse gases such as carbon dioxide.
    </p>
    <p>
        It leads to climate changes such as rising sea levels, more extreme weather events, and impacts on wildlife and ecosystems.
    </p>
    <p>Learn more on 
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_warming" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Wikipedia
        </a>.
    </p>
